Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:09.49,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(890,580)\fad(500,0)\be4}第7話 「繼承者」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個頸圈完全扯不動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且塔克斯還沒展示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發揮這個殺人修煉場特性的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點最叫人害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來吧！要往我身上打什麼波紋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些窩囊廢別想碰到我一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 縮了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 齊貝林大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃招 塔克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波紋亂渦疾走！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(615,625)}Tornado Overdrive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上面來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 齊貝林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖鏈從下面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上下齊發的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺技 天地來蛇殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(700,625)}Hell Heaven Snakill
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鏈雙雕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼…呼吸不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…波紋就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jo…JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧大人 已經遵循您的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他們解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這種事情 太殘酷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子頸骨都斷了 還有氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jo…JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的究極…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的究極…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的究極奧義！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳給JoJo你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 繼承我的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極深僊脈疾走！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(670,625)}Deep Pass Overdrive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 JoJo 我的全部生命能量都傳給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊…齊貝林大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在我的腳下化為肉醬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬…喬斯達先生把塔克斯吊起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊貝林大叔的波紋治癒了他的頸傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 你一個區區的人類想扯開這個頸圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我得到了迪奧大人賜予的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也破壞不了這鋼鐵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕 塔克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那扭曲的精神 醜惡的狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將最深處的靈魂也賣給迪奧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,URRRRRYYYYYYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了 井噴般的強大力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以往的喬斯達先生完全不一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身體流淌著齊貝林大叔的生命波紋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們兩人力量的乘積！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔克斯 我要讓你連骨頭一起從這個世界蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把邪惡的靈魂斬草除根！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠沉睡於歷史的黑暗中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 口出狂言！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淪落到出這種小技倆嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WWWRRRYYYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊貝林先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊貝林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣的結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你…我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 你個大蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是傷心的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打倒迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去破壞石面具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊貝林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對自己的命運滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…年輕的時候結過婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為了追尋石面具丟下了家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我對自己的命運滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人生的最後 我的一切都傳給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…你是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊貝林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶如同時擁有一個摯友與兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而以後 我將活在你的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十九世紀 英國作家威廉·M·薩克雷說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「愛且得到是最幸福的事 愛而失去次之」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:14:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而JoJo則將繼承…他的生存意義與精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 齊貝林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求…求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至…至少放過這孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這位夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是如此希望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「自己的生命可以獻給我們」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但請不要對我的孩子出手」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少這孩子…求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 包括我在內的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會對這孩子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迪奧對天發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 這裏的僕人都是屈服於恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自願把靈魂獻給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像他們一樣 母子一起成為我們的同伴會更幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有煩惱 不會有痛苦 更不會母子成仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請至少放過這孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…寶寶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的 我們不會出手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉孩子的是你這個母親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你自己選擇的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生的樣子有點變化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉上濃濃的陰霾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命地忍耐著悲傷和仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在打倒迪奧之前沒空悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧剛才說要在一晝夜內毀滅這個鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍生人又會產生新的屍生人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那速度堪比鼠疫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上現在到底什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾風騎士鎮還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐他們不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 波克 這麼晚你到哪裏玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當叔 我姐姐呢 鎮裏呢 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事？哪裏沒事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒火沖天啊！說回去就要把你關牛棚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來鎮裏還沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝 亞當叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子啊 小孩子熱騰騰的鮮血真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男人已經變成屍生人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲過老子的快攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來 小鎮已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 屍生人已經開始往郊外蔓延了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來一個屍生人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫旦亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢腿嗎？但是速度太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺！閃電空裂刃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(715,625)}Thunder Split Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都會後仰躲閃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他反而抱著兩敗俱傷的覺悟用頭撞過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 喬納森·喬斯達 我是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒犯了 我是想看看你從齊貝林身上學到多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說齊貝林！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們拜在同一位師傅門下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同通過嚴酷修行 是二十年來的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是史特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是…齊貝林先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這是齊貝林向我們求援的信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道石面具的蹤跡以及其持有者的齊貝林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切內情都寫在上面寄給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是吾師 多配地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是齊貝林的師傅 多配地老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有這樣的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是見面禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 齊貝林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 齊貝林已經去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們再早一點到達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概也會是同樣結局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 迪奧的力量實在是壓倒性的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他擁有強大無匹的邪惡生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用一個晚上 這個鎮就會成為我的囊中物了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:13.89,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I'll be the roundabout
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:17.78,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}The words will make you out 'n' out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:23.11,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:29.44,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.95,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}The music dance and sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:44.79,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}They make the children really ring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:50.24,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:56.81,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.47,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}In and around the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:04.63,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:11.39,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:17.82,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:26.37,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be there with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}中計了 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我史特雷 絕不留手！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}葬送你我不會有任何負罪感！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來吧 JoJo！
